    {
        "content": "<p>Just a note that <code>field_simp</code> is a bit misleading here -- its job is to clear denominators to fractions and that's not actually what you're doing.  A lighter-weight version of the <code>field_simp</code> line is <code>simp (discharger := positivity)</code>.</p>",
        "id": 478610284,
        "sender_full_name": "Heather Macbeth",
        "timestamp": 1729732916
    }
